data.description: Check out this fantastic 2,830 sqft, 3 bdrm, 4bath, multi-level home on a large corner lot. Former model home boasts a sun-filled, open and spacious design. Perfect for hosting those memorable gatherings is the spacious eat-in kitchen with access to a large, covered patio and family room w/ gas fireplace. Open loft area with built-in cabinets overlooks the formal living area.  Retreat to your master bedroom suite with walk-in closet and an on-suite bathroom with double sink vanity, tub, and separate shower. Two more well-sized bedrooms, and main bath upstairs. Oversized 2 car garage with access to half bath and mudroom.  All of this plus a partially finished basement for gym, office, or media room.  Be first to see, won't last.
